    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 10th level, when you hit a creature with your natural weapons while you are @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.gaVd6MJT8Q6PLE9B]{Raging}, the beast within you can curse your target with rabid fury. The target must succeed on a <strong>Wisdom saving throw</strong> (DC equal to 8 + your Constitution modifier + your proficiency bonus) or suffer one of the following effects (your choice):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The target must use its reaction to make a melee attack against another creature of your choice that you can see.</li>\n<li>Target takes <strong>2d12 psychic damage</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>.</p>",
